Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdirilah, Kizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kamu masih mencintai Mizuho,
