Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, aku yang saat itu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mencintai Kizuki\Nyang hanya menatap ke depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu porsi peperoncino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu porsi karbonara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segelas jus grapefruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan buatkan segelas es teh juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}To-Tolong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuho, es tehnya pakai susu, lemon,
