Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Airu, kamu juga ikut, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, enggak dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Hari ini ada syuting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku mau pergi ke suatu tempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selesai!
