Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski agak makan waktu,\Nhasilnya bagus, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, cepat dicicipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana komentarnya? Enak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga makan, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, kudengar Kizuki\Nakan diwawancarai secara khusus.
